  "detailed_description": "Cute meets creepy in this twin-stick-shooter mayhem!<br />\r\nUp to four players can join forces or battle against each other within multiple arenas.<br />\r\nUse a variety of items and spells to defeat hordes of wicked monsters.<br />\r\nBut shooting isn't all; raise the dead to fight for you and triumph!<br />\r\nTen different elements to master: <br />\r\nFire, Frost, Zap, Love, Shadow, Light, Blood, Soul, Plague and Venom -- each with unique added effects to spells and conditional damage multipliers!<br />\r\nSeveral unique thematic arenas to test your skills and strategies, each with a mighty arena champion at the end.",
